      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $x,y\\in \\N$, $y \\ge 3$.\n    Montrer par r{\\'e}\\-cur\\-rence sur $y$ que :\n    $3^x \\equiv 1 (\\mathrm{mod}\\, {2^y}) \\iff 2^{y-2}\\mid x$.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x,y\\in \\N\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(y \\ge 3\\)</span>. Montrer par r<span>é</span>currence sur <span class=\"math inline\">\\(y\\)</span> que : <span class=\"math inline\">\\(3^x \\equiv 1 (\\mathrm{mod}\\, {2^y}) \\iff 2^{y-2}\\mid x\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "7c9a940b-4762-4d86-8658-70206c8f866a",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Trouver tous les couples d'entiers $x,y \\in \\N$ tels que\n    $3^x = 2^y + 1$.",
        "html": "<p>Trouver tous les couples d’entiers <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x,y \\in \\N\\)</span> tels que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(3^x = 2^y + 1\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
